<p>
<lb n="1"/>śrī svasti <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> vēdēbhaśivaśākābdē Ekkali
<lb n="2" break="no"/>kṣitiśēkharaḥ <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> gaṇapatyadhipaḥ
<lb n="3"/>prādāddīpaṁ śrībhīmaśaṁbhavē <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied>
<lb n="4"/>śakava<unclear>rṣa</unclear>mulu 118<unclear>4</unclear> gu nē
<lb n="5" break="no"/>ṇḍu Uttarāyaṇasaṁkrāṁtināṁḍu śrī
<lb n="6" break="no"/>maddākṣārāmamuna śrībhīmēśvarama
<lb n="7" break="no"/>hādēvaraku Ekkaligaṇapatidēvani ko
<lb n="8" break="no"/>ḍku murārigaṇapaya danaku Ā
<lb n="9" break="no"/>yuṣkāmyārtthamugāṁ beṭṭina A
<lb n="10" break="no"/>khaṁḍḍavartti lōhada<unclear>ṁ</unclear>ṇḍu dīpaṁ
<lb n="11"/>Okkaṁṭiki mūṁḍavu Aḍapu
<lb n="12"/>kāmebōyani pūṁṭṭanu nūṁkkabō
<lb n="13" break="no"/>la mārani vasamunaṁ beṭṭina pasu
<lb n="14" break="no"/>lu 50 diṁṭiki dinamokkaṁṭṭiki
<lb n="15"/>tribhuvanāṁkkuśamāneṁḍu ne
<lb n="16" break="no"/>yi Aruvaṁgalavāṁḍu <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g>
</p>

